Google Parent Alphabet Beats Earnings Estimates and Now Has 1 Billion Users 
AdWeek Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Google's new parent company , reported strong third-quarter earnings Thursday, beating estimates with a total revenue of $18.7 billion. The company's six products-Google, YouTube, Android, Google Maps, Google Play and Google Chrome-now...
